<topic template="Default" lasteditedby="rbwinst" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../helpproject.xsd">
  <title translate="true">CSUB Example: Recharge</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">CSUB Example: Recharge</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Recharge in the model comes from rivers that enter the active area of the model from the edge and release water into 18 cells in the top model layer at a rate of 5.5x10</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:8pt; vertical-align:super;" translate="true">-4</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> m/day. The specific cells are colored in the illustration below.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="CSubExampleRechargeCells.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"><title translate="true">CSUB Example: Recharge cells</title></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">First activate the Recharge package in the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MODFLOW_Packages_Dialog_Box" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">MODFLOW Packages and Programs</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> dialog box. Click </text><text styleclass="Strong" translate="true">OK</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> to close the dialog box.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="CSubExampleRechargePackage.png" scale="60.00%" width="470" height="353" styleclass="Image Caption"><title translate="true">CSUB Example: Activating Rechage package</title></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Create a </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Points" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">point</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> object in one of the cells. In the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Object_Properties_Dialog_Box" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Object Properties</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> dialog box, The Z formulas should be set to include just the top layer </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="CSUB_Example_Convertible_Cells" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">as was done when specifying Cell_Type</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">. On the MODFLOW Features tab, specify the times to include all three stress periods and set the rate to 5.5E-4. Click </text><text styleclass="Strong" translate="true">OK</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> to close the dialog box.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="CSubExampleRechargeValues.png" scale="60.00%" width="472" height="352" styleclass="Image Caption"><title translate="true">Recharge Rate</title></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">This specifies one of the recharge boundaries. You could create additional point objects to create the rest of them. However, because all the recharge boundaries will have the same rate there is an easier method to specify them. With the object that defines the recharge boundary still selected, select </text><text styleclass="Strong" translate="true">Object|Edit|Add Point Sections</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> or click the </text><text styleclass="Strong" translate="true">Add point sections</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> </text><image src="AddPoints.bmp" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"><title translate="true">Add Point Sections button</title></image><text styleclass="Image Caption" translate="true"> </text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">button. Then click on each of the other cells that should be recharge cells.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="CSubExampleRechargeCellObjects.png" scale="60.00%" width="457" height="356" styleclass="Image Caption"><title translate="true">CSUB Example: Defining recharge clls</title></image></para>
  </body>
</topic>
